title: Zen Bakery
description: Zen Bakery uses natural and healthier ingredients for baking muffins, cakes, scones, cookies, and rolls. Has fiber cakes, oat bran muffins, carob scones, cinnamon raisin rolls, etc. Supplies to many local markets, like Whole Foods and others. This is their kitchen with a small retail area in front. Hot coffee and tea available.
